<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Asti dvādaśabhūparūpakhacitaprōdbhāsibhūṣāṁcitaśrīpā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>dō bhujanirjjitākhilaripu<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīmatsyavaṁśōdbhavaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmānarjuna
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bhūpatirgguṇanidhistasyādhikaprēyasī tatkīrtyā bhuvi viśrutāsti kama
<lb n="4" break="no"/>lādēvī guṇālaṁkṛtā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śākābdē nidhiśailabhānugaṇitē pauṣē sitāyāṁ
<lb n="5"/>tithau saptamyāṁ śaśivāsarē naraharē<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīsiṁhasailēśituḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Agrē dīpavidīpta<unclear>yē</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nudivasaṁ paṁcāśataṁ sa<supplied reason="omitted">d</supplied>gavāṁ prādātsapratimāṁ ca bhaktimahitā svābhīṣṭa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>saṁsiddhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1279 gunēṁṭi pauṣya śukla saptamiyu sōmavā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ramunāṁḍu Oḍḍavādi Arjunadēvarājula mahādēvi kamalādēvi tana ma
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nōrathasiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni sannidhiyaṁdu nityamunnu Oka A
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kaṁḍadīpamu veluṁguṭaku peṭṭina mōdālu Ēṁbhai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 50 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmu śrī
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

